" alt=\"DC Photobooth Rentals - Wedding Crashers\" width=\"990\" height=\"549\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">That\'s right!  And we\'re just as excited as you are.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">As your wedding date approaches and you are making all those last minute preparations, don\'t forget to reserve a photobooth!  Photobooths at weddings are a simple idea that have been taken to the next level.   Working weddings and other events, we see time and time again that  renting a photobooth is the perfect way to ensure that all of your guests will have a great time.   Some like to sing at weddings, some like to dance, some like to drink, but everyone enjoys throwing on a goofy hat and oversized sunglasses and being silly in front of a camera.  Guests have the opportunity to express themselves however they choose, and have something to take home with them to make your wedding that much more memorable.  And, with a scrapbook provided by DC Photobooth, guests have the opportunity to leave pictures and messages to you and your spouse!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">DC Photobooth has you covered for your wedding photobooth rental.  Shoot us a message to find out more about our packages and start the process of making your big night more memorable for you and all of your guests.</p>','Wedding Season Is Here - Don\'t Forget the Photobooth!','','inherit','open','open','','352-autosave','','','2012-03-27 17:47:14','2012-03-27 17:47:14','',352,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/blog/352-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(207,1,'2012-02-17 06:55:45','2012-02-17 06:55:45','','FAQs','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-3','','','2012-02-17 06:55:45','2012-02-17 06:55:45','',33,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/33-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(208,1,'2012-02-18 07:15:54','2012-02-18 07:15:54','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">frequently asked questions</h1>\n<div class=\"faq-main\">\n\n<div class=\"faq-footer\">Can\'t find the answer to your question below?  Give us a shout and we\'ll be more than happy to answer any questions or concerns you may have.  For any additional questions please call us at 703.898.1702 or <a href=\"/contact\">send us a message!</a> </di\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">How many people can the photo booth fit?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We can fit you and up to 8 of your guests at one time.</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">How can I book a photobooth for my event?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Just give us a call or email us with your questions and your reservation inquiries. We can work through the details together and put together the package that best suits your event. We can’t wait to work with you!</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Is a deposit required to reserve a booth?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes, we require a $100 deposit to reserve your booth for your event date. Your final payment is required one week before the date of your event.</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">What methods of payment are available?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Right now we only accept cash, checks and PayPal.  Contact us for more details.</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">What if I have to cancel or reschedule my event?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We will work with you to reschedule your photo booth rental upon availability.</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Will there be someone at the event to make sure everything runs smoothly?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">We will be there to set up the photo booth before your events starts, and will remain on hand throughout your event to make sure everyone is having a great time and that the photobooth stays stocked and running smoothly.</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Can we customize the printout design?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Certainly! We highly suggest that you work with us to customize background and text that is displayed on your prints. Whether you want to use a logo, names and dates, or your favorite quote, we will do everything that we can to make it happen. Virtually anything is possible with the customization level of our prints.</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Do we need any special kind of hookup or facilities, to set up the photobooth on-site?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">A normal AC power source is all that is needed, preferably within 10-20 feet.</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-question\">Can we get a copy of the images taken by the digital photobooth on a disk?</div>\n<div class=\"faq-answer\">Yes all photobooth rentals include a CD or DVD of all the photos taken at high resolution.</div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-footer\">For any additional questions please call us at 703.898.1702 or <a href=\"/contact\">send us a message!</a> </div>\n\n\n</div>','FAQs','','inherit','open','open','','33-autosave','','','2012-02-18 07:15:54','2012-02-18 07:15:54','',33,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/33-autosave/',0,'revision','',0),(209,1,'2012-02-18 06:48:33','2012-02-18 06:48:33','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">frequently asked questions</h1>','FAQs','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-4','','','2012-02-18 06:48:33','2012-02-18 06:48:33','',33,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/33-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(210,1,'2012-02-18 06:53:49','2012-02-18 06:53:49','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">frequently asked questions</h1>\r\n<div class=\"faq-main\">\r\n\r\n</div>','FAQs','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-5','','','2012-02-18 06:53:49','2012-02-18 06:53:49','',33,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/33-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(211,1,'2012-02-18 06:54:27','2012-02-18 06:54:27','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">frequently asked questions</h1>\r\n<div class=\"faq-main\">\r\n\r\n</div>','FAQs','','inherit','open','open','','33-revision-6','','','2012-02-18 06:54:27','2012-02-18 06:54:27','',33,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/33-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(212,1,'2012-02-18 06:59:10','2012-02-18 06:59:10','<h1 class=\"postTitle page\">frequently asked questions</h1>\r\n<div class