d.\r\n\r\nThe fundraiser was this past Thursday, June 21st.  It was held at the beautiful B. Smith Restaurant in Union Station.  The Safe Coverage Foundation rented out the main dining area of the restaurant and held a silent auction of signed sports, music and movie memorabilia to raise funds for the foundation.  We made some individual bids while we were there and ended up winning!\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter  postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/IMG_20120621_212349-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at WeddingWire World\" width=\"405\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px; text-align: center;\">Here are some of our favorite images from the night!</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px; text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-580 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_022821-1921269247-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-578\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_015652-1921269085-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" />  <img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-577\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_015511-1921269065-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">These two were so cute, and loved the photobooth so much that they tried it out twice!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-573 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_004521-1921268903-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-578\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_015842-1921269108-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" />  <img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-577\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_012300-1921268987-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-581 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_023017-1921269261-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-578\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_005438-1921268957-O-688x1024