tion\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/20000101_095531-1984764055-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"469\" height=\"698\" />\r\n<div style=\"float: left; width: 50%;\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.weddingwire.com\">WeddingWire</a>, the leading technology company in the wedding industry, held their inaugural WeddingWire World conference at the Kennedy Center this past Monday, July 23rd. The company is designed to help local and national wedding vendors better market themselves to engaged couples during their wedding planning. They have an array of invaluable tools for engaged couples to help in every facet of their wedding planning, and provide a suite of organizational material to wedding vendors to help them gain exposure and run their business. WeddingWire World, open exclusively to WeddingWire members, was an entire day full of guest speakers, education, networking and fun aimed at educating wedding professionals on how to grow their business. DC Photobooth was lucky enough to provide our photobooth for the day to make the event more memorable to its guests. We met several fellow wedding professionals and had a great time. Here are some of our favorites from the day!\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter  postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/ww-world.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at WeddingWire World\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px;\"></div>','WeddingWire World','','inherit','open','open','','636-revision-6','','','2012-07-25 02:01:57','2012-07-25 02:01:57','',636,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/blog/636-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(655,1,'2012-07-25 01:24:07','2012-07-25 01:24:07','','WeddingWire World','','inherit','open','open','','636-revision-3','',''