ext-align: left;\">The Wedding Salon did a great job.  This was, by far, one of the more beautiful and well decorated bridal events we have ever been to.  Several luxury wedding vendors were in attendance, and brought elaborate set ups to show off their products to the brides and their friends and family.  It was quite a sight.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">We were in a great spot during the event and were able to show off our photobooth really well.  And the guests were loving it!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Some cool pictures from the event are below.  To view all the photobooth images from the show, <a title=\"Event Photos\" href=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/event-photos/\">click here</a>!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-740 postimg\" style=\"margin-top: 40px;\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9239.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"900\" height=\"735\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We had a blast hanging out with other vendors and getting to meet so many excited brides and their friends and family.  They really had a great time trying out our photobooth and checking our some of our example designs and scrapbook packages.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Here are some of our favorites from the events:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9197.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-737 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9197-233x300.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"233\" height=\"300\" /></a>   <a href=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9208.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-747 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9208-295x300.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"295\" height=\"300\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/20000101035028.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-749 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/20000101035028-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-736 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9195.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"693\" height=\"462\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-738 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9222.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"810\" height=\"599\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-751 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/20000101032652-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9168.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-734 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9168-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a>  <a href=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9189.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-735 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/MG_9189-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-750 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/20000101022956-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We had an awesome time at the Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show on Monday!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you missed out on this show this year, we would definitely recommend checking it out next year.  It\'s a gorgeous show, and a great way to meet so many wedding professionals!</p>','Washington Wedding Salon Bridal Show','','publish','open','open','','washington-wedding-salon-bridal-show','','\nhttp://www.dc-photobooth.com/event-photos/','2012-09-14 19:35:33','2012-09-14 19:35:33','',0,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/?p=720',0,'post','',0),(669,1,'2012-07-25 02:01:28','2012-07-25 02:01:28','<img class=\"wp-image-574 postimg alignleft\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 15px;\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_004632-1921268910-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"469\" height=\"698\" />\r\n<div style=\"float: left; width: 50%;\">\r\n\r\nDC Photobooth had the incredible opportunity to be a part of a fundraiser for the <a title=\"Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" href=\"http://www.antoinebethea.com/safe-coverage-foundation\" target=\"_blank\">Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation</a>, a charity organization founded by Indianapolis Colts free safety Antoine Bethea to help students reach their dreams of obtaining higher education.  The program hopes to build a connection between inner city high school students and local universities by organizing campus tours and meetings with college professors and faculty, and providing lap tops or iPads to in need students.  We were very thankful to be invited and to be given the opportunity to help the organization succeed.\r\n\r\nThe fundraiser was this past Thursday, June 21st.  It was held at the beautiful B. Smith Restaurant in Union Station.  The Safe Coverage Foundation rented out the main dining area of the restaurant and held a silent auction of signed sports, music and movie memorabilia to raise funds for the foundation.  We made some individual bids while we were there and ended up winning!\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter  postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/IMG_20120621_212349-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at WeddingWire World\" width=\"405\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px; text-align: center;\">Here are some of our favorite images from the night!</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px; text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-580 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_022821-1921269247-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-578\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_015652-1921269085-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" />  <img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-577\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_015511-1921269065-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">These two were so cute, and loved the photobooth so much that they tried it out twice!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-573 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_004521-1921268903-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-578\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_015842-1921269108-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" />  <img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-577\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_012300-1921268987-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-581 postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_023017-1921269261-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"670\" height=\"997\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-578\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_005438-1921268957-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" />  <img class=\"postimg size-large wp-image-577\" title=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/20000101_024620-1921269414-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at Fundraiser for Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Foundation\" width=\"464\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DC Photobooth was so honored to be invited to this fundraiser. We were more than happy to offer our services to help make the event a success. Plus we won some great memorabilia!</p>\r\n<p style=\"width: 700px; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: auto; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: auto; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"alignnone postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooths - Premiere photobooth rental company in the DC Metro Region\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/themes/liquorice/images/logos/glasses-mustache-medium-website.png\" alt=\"DC Photobooths - Premiere photobooth rental company in the DC Metro Region\" width=\"160\" height=\"120\" /></p>','Antoine Bethea Safe Coverage Fundraiser 6.21.2012','','inherit','open','open','','572-revision-47','','','2012-07-25 02:01:28','2012-07-25 02:01:28','',572,'http://www.dc-photobooth.com/blog/572-revision-47/',0,'revision','',0),(670,1,'2012-07-25 02:20:03','2012-07-25 02:20:03','<img class=\"wp-image-574 postimg alignleft\" style=\"float: left; margin-right: 15px;\" title=\"DC Photobooth at WeddingWire World\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/20000101_095531-1984764055-O-688x1024.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at WeddingWire World\" width=\"469\" height=\"698\" />\r\n<div style=\"float: left; width: 50%;\">\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.weddingwire.com\" target=\"_blank\">WeddingWire</a>, the leading technology company in the wedding industry, held their inaugural WeddingWire World conference at the Kennedy Center this past Monday, July 23rd. The company is designed to help local and national wedding vendors better market themselves to engaged couples during their wedding planning. They have an array of invaluable tools for engaged couples to help in every facet of their wedding planning, and provide a suite of organizational material to wedding vendors to help them gain exposure and run their business. \r\n\r\nWeddingWire World, open exclusively to WeddingWire members, was an entire day full of guest speakers, education, networking and fun aimed at educating wedding professionals on how to grow their business. DC Photobooth was lucky enough to provide our photobooth for the day to make the event more memorable to its guests. We met several fellow wedding professionals and had a great time. \r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter  postimg\" title=\"DC Photobooth at WeddingWire World\" src=\"http://www.dc-photobooth.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/ww-world.jpg\" alt=\"DC Photobooth at WeddingWire World\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px;\"></div>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px; text-align: center;\">Here are some of our favorites from the day!</div>\r\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 20px; text-align: center;\"></div>\r\n<p style=